_sText:
Hello,

Firstly, thank you very much for downloading my first map and i hope you enjoy playing on it as much as i did making it.

Obviously, this was my first map, so please guys, don't be expecting a "valve-like" master piece. I made this map one day after installing hammer
hence some of the poor textures and skybox.

Prefabs i used : 

1) de_dust2 door was made by valve, i have only copied this to my map
2) guardpost was downloaded from fps banana but has been modified for this map by me (Dalphia)
3) weapon dispensers were also from fps banana


Please, if you want to use any original ideas from this map (including layout) please email me "nanomanxxx@hotmail.com" and also
please recognise  work that was developed by me.

Have fun 

Oh, almost forgot, Please post all constructive feedback to me on fps banana (username = dalphia) or at my email address (nanomanxxx@hotmail.com)

Cheers and enjoy !!

Dalphia

Once again, i only want feedback that will make me a better mapper, no "this sucks" alright. Only constructive feedback :D
